content.rendered:
Glimpses of our recent Northern Emirates Seminar that took place on 3rd November at Ras Al Khaimah. Hosted by Hitachi Cooling & Heating MEA and Technical & Trading Est. (TTE) the event focused on the latest products from Hitachi – the ducted split and VRF, highlighting their latest technology and unique features.

The products on display had features such as Wide Capacity Range up to 72 HP, Best-in-Class EER up to 4.85 @ T1 and 3.70 @ T3, Uninterrupted Operation in Case of Power Failure & many more
